text: Károly Kocsis (born 27 July 1929) is a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Debrecen
